### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَلَمَّا بَلَغَ أَشُدَّهُۥ وَٱسْتَوَىٰٓ ءَاتَيْنَـٰهُ حُكْمًا وَعِلْمًا ۚ وَكَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ</span>

### English

And when he reached full strength and maturity, We gave him wisdom and knowledge. This is how We reward the good-doers.